data.name: label11.Text
data.value: 1 .Delete Emails: Select an email and click the trash icon to delete it. 2 .Archive Emails: Click the archive button to remove emails from the inbox but keep them for later. 3 .Labels and Folders: You can create labels (folders) to organize emails. Select an email, click on the label icon, and either create a new label or assign it to an existing one.
